export default function Piano() { const pianoText = [ "Piano-playing is my main artistic background, and has been a central part of my artistic identity since I started playing when I was 6 years old. I played on a high level as a teenager, and participated in a few competitions. In my 20’s I abandoned the piano for a while. In later years, since I started teaching piano, I have taken up my piano playing again, and enjoy playing a wide variety of musical styles - especially the transcendental piano works of the romantic era and beyond. Here’s a little selection." ]; return (

{pianoText}

); } /* Piano-playing is my main artistic background, and has been a central part of my artistic identity since I started playing when I was 6 years old. I played on a high level as a teenager, and participated in a few competitions. In my 20’s I abandoned the piano for a while. In later years, since I started teaching piano, I have taken up my piano playing again, and enjoy playing a wide variety of musical styles - especially the transcendental piano works of the romantic era and beyond. Here’s a little selection. */
